					"uidString" : "0iml4NF5QvW1nVU8MedJag=="
				},
				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "GT4Amiga incluye un ensamblador 68000 basado en **vasm** (sintaxis Motorola). Cada snippet `amiga68k` tiene botones **Assemble** y **Run on FS-UAE**. Al pulsar *Assemble* se compila el código y se muestra si hay errores; al pulsar *Run on FS-UAE* se envía el ejecutable al emulador y se captura la salida por el puerto serie."
			},
			{
				"__type" : "textSnippet",
				"children" : {
					"__type" : "snippets",
					"items" : [ ]
				},
				"createEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"createTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-06-27T20:34:30.493868+02:00"
					}
				},
				"editEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"editTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-06-27T20:34:30.493868+02:00"
					}
				},
				"uid" : {
					"__type" : "uid",
					"uidString" : "bJs7ghMNQTuOLqdAQMl0zA=="
				},
				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "## Ejemplo 1 — Programa mínimo\n\nEl programa más pequeño posible: no hace nada y retorna al sistema operativo con código de salida 0. En AmigaOS los programas retornan un código en `d0` (0 = éxito)."
			},
			{
				"__type" : "amiga68kSnippet",
				"children" : {
					"__type" : "snippets",
					"items" : [ ]
				},
				"createEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"createTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-06-27T20:34:35.111761+02:00"
					}
				},
				"editEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"editTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-06-27T20:34:35.111761+02:00"
					}
				},
				"uid" : {
					"__type" : "uid",
					"uidString" : "3EnC7o2uQgK/ME3pkDNozg=="
				},
				"code" : "        SECTION code,CODE\n\nstart:\n        moveq   #0,d0       ; código de salida 0 = éxito\n        rts                 ; retornar al sistema operativo\n\n        END start"
			},
			{
				"__type" : "textSnippet",
				"children" : {
					"__type" : "snippets",
					"items" : [ ]
				},
				"createEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"createTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-06-27T20:34:42.275554+02:00"
					}
				},
				"editEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"editTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-06-27T20:34:42.275554+02:00"
					}
				},
				"uid" : {
					"__type" : "uid",
					"uidString" : "3XIQCXaXSguuLG/Xjkl9XQ=="
				},
				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "Pulsa **Assemble** — deberías ver `OK — N bytes`. Si hay un error de sintaxis, el mensaje de vasm aparecerá en el área de salida.\n\n## Ejemplo 2 — Aritmética básica\n\nEl 68000 tiene ocho registros de datos (`d0`–`d7`) y ocho de dirección (`a0`–`a7`). `MOVE`, `ADD` y `SUB` son las instrucciones más comunes. El sufijo `.l`, `.w` o `.b` indica tamaño: *longword* (32 bit), *word* (16 bit) o *byte* (8 bit)."
			},
			{
				"__type" : "amiga68kSnippet",
				"children" : {
					"__type" : "snippets",
					"items" : [ ]
				},
				"createEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"createTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-06-27T20:34:46.51761+02:00"
					}
				},
				"editEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"editTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-06-27T20:34:46.51761+02:00"
					}
				},
				"uid" : {
					"__type" : "uid",
					"uidString" : "MY9KHY9FRcqqADOre948JA=="
				},
				"code" : "        SECTION code,CODE\n\nstart:\n        moveq   #10,d0      ; d0 = 10\n        moveq   #32,d1      ; d1 = 32\n        add.l   d1,d0       ; d0 = d0 + d1 = 42\n        sub.l   #2,d0       ; d0 = d0 - 2 = 40\n        rts                 ; retorna con d0 = 40\n\n        END start"
			},
			{
				"__type" : "textSnippet",
				"children" : {
					"__type" : "snippets",
					"items" : [ ]
				},
				"createEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"createTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-06-27T20:34:51.637202+02:00"
					}
				},
				"editEmail" : {
